## Test Structure Tree ({{ doc.scope }})

```
{{ doc.test_tree.root }}
│
{% for fld in doc.test_tree.fields %}
{%- set is_last_field = loop.last -%}
{%- set field_prefix = '└──' if is_last_field else '├──' -%}
{%- set child_indent = '    ' if is_last_field else '│   ' -%}
{{ field_prefix }} {{ fld.field }} — {{ fld.status }}
{% for sc in fld.scenarios %}
{%- set sc_prefix = '└──' if loop.last else '├──' -%}
{%- set mark = '✓' if sc.covered else '✗' -%}
{%- set ref_text = '' -%}
{%- if sc.covered and sc.get('test_ref') -%}
  {%- set ref_text = ' (' ~ sc.test_ref.path ~ (':' ~ (sc.test_ref.line | string) if sc.test_ref.get('line') else '') ~ ')' -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- set partial_text = ('  [' ~ sc.partial_note ~ ']') if sc.get('partial_note') else '' -%}
{{ child_indent }}{{ sc_prefix }} {{ mark }} {{ sc.description }}{{ ref_text }}{{ partial_text }}
{% endfor %}
{% if not is_last_field %}
│
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
```

